  - [projects](file:///E:/uiChina_Web/China_Web_FE/src/views/admin/config/entityConfigs.js#L308-L340)
  - [project_category_items](file:///E:/uiChina_Web/China_Web_FE/src/views/admin/config/entityConfigs.js#L341-L374)
